<SYNC Start=746333><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=746368><P Class=ENCC>
시리우스도 보이네요
<SYNC Start=748102><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=748153><P Class=ENCC>
ridiculus리디큘러스도 있군요<br>
